title: Purchase Request Form
description: Use this form to request an advance or reimbursement for any expenses related to the AI Business Group (ABG). Be sure to include a clear description of the purchase, the amount needed, and upload any receipts or supporting documents to help us process your request efficiently.

title: Leadership Application
description: If selected for a leadership position, you will receive a more detailed description of your role, along with an overview of expectations during our leadership onboarding meeting. These positions require a greater time commitment and stronger leadership qualities compared to general membership. You will also have significantly more autonomy and responsibility within the club.
